<!--
  English Keyed strings emitted by the adapter assembly. Def label/instruction/tone text stays inline
  in 1.6/Defs and is localized through DefInjected in non-English languages.

  Outlook/adjective text is duplicated as an English Keyed source even though the pure mapper carries
  the same fallback. The fallback keeps a partially-installed language playable; Keyed keeps all normal
  prompt text on RimWorld's localization path.
-->
